summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Corporation Counsel to incur an expenditure in the sum of Fifty (50) Dollars against the General Fund, in the employment of necessary assistance in preparation of transcripts of record covering the issuance and sale of $460,000 Seattle Refunding Bond of 1911, and in bringing up the date of sale transcript in re $1,000,000 Park, $400,000 Garbage, $100,000 Light and $46,000 Georgetown Funding bonds.
